column5: Was down at the marina this morning for my morning walk and there it was.  First thing that came to me was,,,,,,,,,,,,,  TERRYS YAK  I looked on you tube to see if I could find it in action, but no luck.  It,s got a 9.6 hp motor. It,s water jet propelled. Like the sea doos.
Try googling surfango adventurer jet powered kayak - quite a few returns there!  One has a 45 hp setup.  Michael
Thanks Michael  Ok  So let the bidding begin  http://www.ebay.com/bhp/jet-kayak
